  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<ul><li>To assist the Project Manager or Project Engineer in the daily execution of work.</li></ul><ul><li>To supervise the work of sub-contractors and in-house workers.</li></ul><ul><li>To work closely with other site operations staff to meet the project schedule.</li></ul><ul><li>Ensure installation is carried out as per construction drawings.</li></ul><ul><li>To monitor the progress and quality of work being performed by workers.</li></ul><ul><li>Ensure that works are executed within an acceptable standard of workmanship.</li></ul><ul><li>Plan, schedule, and coordinate polymer application projects, ensuring timely delivery and adherence to specifications.</li></ul><ul><li>Attend the daily tool-box meeting and convey clear instruction accordingly.</li></ul><ul><li>Implement safety procedures, ensure regulatory compliance, and manage incident responses.</li></ul><ul><li>Update clients on progress, address concerns, and maintain project documentation.</li></ul><ul><li>Understand and ensure compliance in project requirement and scope of work.</li></ul>",
